ComicInfo.Summary:
Dizzy and the rest of The Rollers have had a quiet couple of days, tracking any possible Negatrix activity and getting Dizzy ready for the big skating competition. But as Dizzy's confidence in her abilities climbs, arrogance becomes a mask for self-doubt, to the detriment of her friends. Even as Dizzy starts to doubt herself, and pushes her pals away, she realizes that Mayor Fox is infected by the Negatrixes and is spreading their negativity all over town! But before she can get her thoughts in order, Dizzy discovers a dark, unexpected secret behind her 'Burb Defender identity at the worst possible time... when her powers run out of charge...
